                            <comment id="13020850" author="atm" created="Sun, 17 Apr 2011 19:23:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Trivial patch to remove the absolute path to &lt;tt&gt;kinit&lt;/tt&gt;, and instead rely on &lt;tt&gt;kinit&lt;/tt&gt; being in the &lt;tt&gt;PATH&lt;/tt&gt; of the process.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13021098" author="owen.omalley" created="Mon, 18 Apr 2011 16:48:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is at the very least an incompatible change, since any site that doesn&apos;t have kinit on the hdfs and mapred account&apos;s path will break.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;That said, I think it is the right direction.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Please update the release note field in the jira to describe that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
